*   `justify-between`: Justify items evenly between the start and end of the container.
*   `justify-around`: Justify items evenly between the start and end of the container, with equal space around each item.
*   `justify-evenly`: Justify items evenly between the start and end of the container, with equal space around each item.

Example:
